         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 1926, recto: (1) Thotsythmis, son of Pasemis, son of (2) Thotsythmis, of the silver of poll of (3) Jeme in year 23, among the men of (4) Snachomneus, 2 staters / 1 / 2 again. (5) Written in year 23, Mesore 10. (6) He is a dead man. [translation of line 6 from Ritner, Enchoria 15]</ab>
